title: #92Noon: IanLeonard/Leber/RonJohnson
description: FOX9's Chief Meteorologist Ian Leonard is in studio during the first hour, Leber makes his weekly appearance in the middle, then Ron Johnson drops by to chat football and share stories about his late father Ron Sr.
